              h1.h3.mb-3.text-nowrap
                | Your messages
                span.d-inline-block.align-middle.bg-faded-success.text-success.fs-ms.fw-medium.rounded-1.py-1.px-2.ms-2 1
              .mb-3
                a(href='#message-compose' data-bs-toggle='collapse').btn.btn-translucent-primary
                  i.ai-plus.me-2
                  | Compose
            
            // Message compose form
